籤詩版本二:
Umgwaqo uyingozi, amahhashi namadoda ayajaha, futhi amasosha asenkingeni enkulu lapho elahlekile.
Ulwandle luphakeme, kuphuka umoya namagagasi, isikebhe siphukile, ilanga liyashona, izimbali ziyafa, isibhakabhaka siyawa, nesithwathwa siyawa Win: bear.棹: isigwedlo.
詩意:
Le hexagram ifana nesikebhe esibhidliza ulwandle.
Qaphela zonke izingozi.
解曰: Isikole esidala nesidala. Ethule futhi engenasici. Asikho isidingo sokufuna iseluleko. Hamba ngokukhululeka.
籤詩故事一:
◇Inkosi yaseChu Yin Ling yalahleka
Ekuqaleni kuka-202 BC, amabutho amaHan angu-400,000 avela ezinhlangothini ezintathu azungeza ibutho lika-Xiang Yu eGaixia, elaliswele ukudla. ngebutho likaHan. Leli qhinga lezengqondo "lokuvinjezelwa nhlangothi zonke" labangela ukuthi ibutho lika-Xiang Yu lilahlekelwe isimilo.
Ngakho-ke u-Xiang Yu wahola abagibeli bamahhashi abangaphezu kuka-800 futhi wanquma ukugqashuka, kuyilapho ibutho le-Han lilandela eduze no-Guan Ying kanye namahhashi angu-5,000. Ngemva kokuwela umfula i-Huai, amabutho ka-Xiang Yu ayesesele abantu abayikhulu kuphela.
U-Xiang yu uduke eYinling wacela umlimi oseceleni komgwaqo indlela eya emfuleni, ngokungalindelekile walandela indlela ekhonjwe ikhehla wagcina egcwele ixhaphozi okwenza kwaba nzima ukunyakaza, wacishe wadlulwa uLiu. Ibutho lika-Bang. U-Xiang Yu wagcina efikile eWujiang futhi wayazi ukuthi isimo sasiphelile. Ebona abadala baseJiangdong engenamahloni, wazibulala.
聖意: Umndeni kanye nendlu bakhathazekile ngezinhlekelele zabo, ukufuna imali nokubhidliza ibhizinisi, umshado awuhlali isikhathi eside, uLiujia uyingozi, abahamba ngezinyawo bavimbe amasimu. Konakele iminyundu. Kulinyazwe imfuyo eyisithupha, abantu abalahlekile, amacala omphakathi. Ukulahlekelwa Ukufuduka Impahla Elahlekile Ukugula Akulungile ukuthumela ithuna entabeni.
